rd; margin: 0px;\">\n加入如下内容并保存：</p><p data-lake-id=\"c47b3645eef9467b3e9cd0edf96bc7e0\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" id=\"19a45c97\" data-language=\"plain\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 16px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><pre class=\"cm-s-default\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">deny 66.249.79.84 ;</span></span></pre></div></div></div><p data-lake-id=\"5c1fd87ddb747f109e48d362320dab92\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"0672ad164c772274146b0ef50f291bd6\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">在nginx的配置文件nginx.conf中加入如下配置，可以放到http, server, location, limit_except语句块，需要注意相对路径，本例当中nginx.conf，guolv_ip.conf在同一个目录中。</p><p data-lake-id=\"38ccb2e47c59ccefd3584820b3e8c14d\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" id=\"6dbbcdd7\" data-language=\"plain\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 16px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><pre class=\"cm-s-default\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">include guolv_ip.conf;</span></span></pre></div></div></div><p data-lake-id=\"fa11019633606219d796014b1322ba3a\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"2b79413ed6fb0def378fa8106ee1067b\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px